Osborne Says Banks Let Down Shareholders, Customers, Country

-- B y   R o b e r t   H u t t o n
-- 
2011-10-03T11:18:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/osborne-says-banks-let-down-shareholders-customers-country.html
U.K. Chancellor of the Exchequer
 George Osborne  attacked banks during his speech to the
 Conservative Party ’s annual conference today in Manchester,
northwest  England .  “They let down their customers, they let down their
shareholders and they let down the country,” Osborne said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
